
* 2008-06-01
	Removed the PreCST monad for now, as the initial code base should be as small as possible.
	It is easy to inject the parse results back into PreCST.
	As a consequence, the NameSupply (implemented using unsafePerformIO and IORefs) has been
	removed as well.
	As long as you stay within the ParserMonad, each AST element still has an unique id.
	
* 2008-05-29 
  Add a top-level module acting as facade (Language.C)

* 2008-05-29
	Added a CCWrapper module (primarily for convenience).

* 2008-05-26 
  Renaming / Hierarchical Modules
  see src/refactor.receipt